metadata.name: Rebel Sloths #1
metadata.description: Rebel Sloths is a collection of 7,979 hand drawn and generated NFTs for all the different types of rebels out there. What kind of rebel are you? Let all of us rebels embrace the chill life. Be passionate. Be Brave. Stand for what you believe. But remember it doesn't come to you in a day (unless you join the Rebel Sloth community ðŸš€). Think of your favorite rebel. Now think about their story. Did it span a day? month? year? It's a lifetime. Join us in taking the most chill first step to the moon!
